race.description: Ladbrokes Million Dollar Chase Semi Final 2 H
race.comment: ZIPPING XADEN (7) recorded a 16 length win (29.45) in a NG last time at this track. Has an unbeaten record from this draw, scoring two times. Looks a leading chance on best. ZIPPING ARIEL (2) tends to take a while to wind up, missing the placings two back but running on to last time finishing second (29.66) in a NG at this track. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Expecting another good run. DYNAMIC DRUMMER (8) missed the frame latest (30.09) when fourth over 520m at this track in a Grade 5. Has already won three times from this draw. Looks one of the chances. MOSSY BOOTS (1) is in form and worth thought again.
